name: DogeShiba
description: DogeShiba is the fusion between the two most successful meme coins of all time, and the first Shiba launched on the new DogeChain. DogeShiba aims to directly support both DogeCoin and DogeChain through a series of utilities, the DogeShiba Ecosystem. DogeShiba also has one of the largest communities on the entire DogeChain, with the common goal of bringing back the old school values of meme coins.
